OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FData from NHS England shows more than
OL,8,F57,000 women received treatment in the
OL,9,Flast year, that's up a third compared
OL,10,Fto the year before.
OL,12,FIt can feel like "the end of the
OL,13,Fworld" one woman who experienced told
OL,14,FITV News.
OL,16,FWe've been given permission to film at
OL,17,Fthe Ribblemere Mother and Baby Unit in
OL,18,FLancashire, a psychiatric ward where
OL,19,Fwomen are treated with their babies.
