OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FThe Royal College of Psychiatrists
OL,8,Festimates that up to 1,200 mothers
OL,9,Fexperience psychosis each year in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales.
OL,12,FElinor Davies was one of them.
OL,14,FShe was admitted to Ribblemere Mother
OL,15,Fand Baby Unit after the birth of her
OL,16,Fson.
