OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,F"You feel quite alone, it's quite an
OL,8,Fisolating experience. It's way more
OL,9,Fthan depression and anxiety, it's like
OL,10,Fthe end of the world." she told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,FHer son is now nearly four years old,
OL,14,Fand she supports other women, through
OL,15,Fthe charity Action on Postpartum
OL,16,FPsychosis.
OL,18,F"He doesn't remember being in hospital
OL,19,Fwith me, but I'm very open about it"
OL,20,FEli told ITV News.
