OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,F"Although it might sound scary that
OL,8,Fmummy was hospital, I think it's
OL,9,Freally important for him to know I got
OL,10,Fbetter with the help of everyone
OL,11,Faround me in the hospital."
OL,13,FThe pandemic and the cost-of-living
OL,14,Fcrisis have driven a rise in all
OL,15,Fmental health problems.
OL,17,FThe increase in pregnant women and new
OL,18,Fmothers getting support is partly down
OL,19,Fto improved services, but also
OL,20,Freflects the growing demand.
