OL,7,F"Our deepest condolences go out to
OL,8,FKath's family and loved ones,"
OL,9,FHerefordshire and Worcestershire
OL,10,FHealth and Care NHS Trust told ITV
OL,11,FNews.
OL,13,F"We fully accept the findings of the
OL,14,Finquest and have conducted a full
OL,15,Freview in order to find out what has
OL,16,Fhappened and if we can make changes to
OL,17,Fprevent deaths in the future."
