OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FClaire Murdoch, NHS England's National
OL,8,FMental Health Director says: "Our
OL,9,Fspecialist teams across the country
OL,10,Fare highly trained and have many
OL,11,Feffective approaches to successful
OL,12,Ftreatment, so if you are pregnant or
OL,13,Fhave given birth in the last two years
OL,14,Fand are struggling with your mental
OL,15,Fhealth then please do not hesitate to
OL,16,Fask your GP for support, the NHS is
OL,17,Fhere to help."
