OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FAnyone can experience maternal mental
OL,8,Fhealth problems, but campaigners say
OL,9,Fsome are less likely to receive the
OL,10,Fcare they need, for example black and
OL,11,Fbrown women, young mothers, and those
OL,12,Fliving in poverty.
OL,14,FNHS England says every part of England
OL,15,Fnow has a specialist mental health
OL,16,Fteam offering women with moderate to
OL,17,Fsevere or complex mental health needs
OL,18,Fsupport.
