OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FBut experts say despite the increase
OL,8,Fin services in recent years, staff
OL,9,Fshortages and unstable funding are
OL,10,Fhampering efforts.
OL,12,F"There's huge demand for care and
OL,13,Fservices," says Dr Livia Martucci from
OL,14,Fthe Royal College of Psychiatrists.
OL,16,F"Even though services have expanded,
OL,17,Fthey are stretched. And sometimes they
OL,18,Fstruggle to meet demand."
