OL,3,C'It's like the end of the world':
OL,4,CSurge in new mums getting mental
OL,5,Chealth care
OL,7,FHealth minister, Maria Caulfield, told
OL,8,FITV News the government is "committed
OL,9,Fto ensuring these services are
OL,10,Favailable to every new mother who
OL,11,Fneeds them, no matter where they live
OL,12,Fin England."
OL,14,FShe continued: "The government has
OL,15,Falso significantly increased spending
OL,16,Fon mental health to support these
OL,17,Fambitions."
OL,19,FFor the sake of the next generation,
OL,20,Feveryone agrees, it is vital we invest
OL,21,Fin the health of their mothers.
